### Status
GET http://localhost:8080/api/study/status

### Explain a concept
POST http://localhost:8080/api/study/explain
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "What is Spring AI ChatClient?",
  "level": "beginner",
  "goal": "explain it in an interview"
}

### Generate a quiz
POST http://localhost:8080/api/study/quiz
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "topic": "Spring AI structured output",
  "difficulty": "beginner",
  "numberOfQuestions": 3
}

### Generate flashcards
POST http://localhost:8080/api/study/flashcards
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "topic": "Spring Boot profiles",
  "level": "beginner",
  "count": 5
}
